被反送中感動/影響想出一分力既 所以我又唔會去質疑佢呢樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"落先=生人霸死地 個區唔係你架<br />\n落後=空降食撚屎 大黨大撚晒？<br />\n<br />\n泛民就係原罪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"又玩斷章取義呀？ 講緊佢一早落插完旗唔撚做野呀<br />\n你鍾意屈冇所謂呀 睇下自己泛民咁多年做過d咩先學人屌選民啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"你想比政績？ 咁你不如列舉下另一個做左d乜？"},{"pid":"7c75b2df5eb2cc252e9a17e136cc32cf2e62868f","tid":1745213,"uid":43991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"吳可淇係手足黎<br />\n<br />\n利申 識佢"},{"pid":"67d86b77ed079ee712fb082f45c13d690c61836e","tid":1745213,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"陳浩天咪最大嗰隻鬼囉<br />\n你睇下佢氹到碌撚幾掂"},{"pid":"85e4c16d70be37bac62cfd77ef3164f5901ef400","tid":1745213,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d86b77ed079ee712fb082f45c13d690c61836e","tid":1745213,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"陳浩天咪最大嗰隻鬼囉<br />\n你睇下佢氹到碌撚幾掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fc6dbe107d337bbcb1160fe90635c84a64bff7","tid":1745213,"uid":193364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18bb5bf0e20d7b0b98f53916db6e0d66b6f6c995","tid":1745213,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"大圍區區選-𠝹票人鄒家成<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744973</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先想講大圍美林3號嘅鄒家成<br />\n作為佢嘅兄弟<br />\n我必需要承認<br />\n無錯，鄒家成個樣係似狗<br />\n但佢係百份百手足黎<br />\n唔應該以貌取人<br />\n<br />\n我唔可以講太仔細<br />\n但佢真係一個真。勇者<br />\n<br />\n個post話佢用民族紅色做底色<br />\n話成仔係扮手足扮勇武<br />\n我想回應返樓豬兩張相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nvdxe44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvdxe44.png&h=92315a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohFLAe4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohFLAe4.png&h=c39de2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，佢隻腳點傷唔通又要周圍講？<br />\n<br />\n第三，我聽過成仔同吳定霖傾計<br />\n成仔問佢論壇去唔去<br />\n吳定霖態度閪撚到呢<br />\n根本無當過成仔係同路人<br />\n吳定霖仲夠膽死咁講：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「我無話你界我票，<br />\n我只話你分薄咗我嘅票源。」</span><br />\n聽完哩句我就知<br />\n吳定霖真係低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時就話和勇不分<br />\n一講到政治利益<br />\n吳定霖就現晒形<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPK8x0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPK8x0k.jpg&h=401fb780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n我陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄒家成facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/owenchowkashing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fowenchowkashing%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=0e3ae602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/owenchowkashing/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n康城環保南3號嘅吳可淇<br />\n<br />\n第一，有人話佢係鬼<br />\n因為佢曾經做過支拿公司嘅高層<br />\n「我承認係做過支那公司，但係8月底已經離職，好多人為左份工，為左份糧忍受白色恐怖，而家我要放棄10年的工作同成果，一啲都唔容易。<br />\n<br />\n出嚟選為咩？就係為良知為香港下一代自由民主。」<br />\n<br />\n第二，佢係好遲先出黎選<br />\n「唔信將軍澳民生關注組，佢哋就係偽民主，反送中，一地兩檢全部棄權，仲有不同人都有同建制拉上關係，然後無限澄清，仲有佢哋召集人展j根本一啲都唔可信，就係因為我係將來康城既街坊，所以我唔可以唔理，最後一刻決定出嚟選。」<br />\n<br />\n第三，我敢保證佢唔係鬼<br />\n因為我親眼睇住佢係某個地方救人<br />\n最後真係救到<br />\n我諗連比佢救嘅手足都唔會知佢係候選人<br />\n因為佢嘅作風係自己救人自己知就算<br />\n佢唔會周圍同人講<br />\n哩d先係真正抗爭者會做嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n佢同我有一齊做過小小支援手足嘅行為<br />\n佢真係盡心盡力默默咁做<br />\n佢唔似姓姜姓陳咁<br />\n周圍同人講自己嘅功績<br />\n吳可淇一直就只有默默咁做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4FvMiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4FvMiX.jpg&h=ac9f5918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳可淇facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%97%E5%90%B3%E5%8F%AF%E6%B7%87-107083390709670/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%25B7%2587-107083390709670%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=acb6dec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%97%E5%90%B3%E5%8F%AF%E6%B7%87-107083390709670/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家可以大力支持我地</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"呢個吳可淇<br />\n<br />\n我竟然有一刻......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得佢有幾分似東方昇<br />\n屌我係咪要驗眼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f26ca6954388c4c11703ef07d757536b9223c47","tid":1745213,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}